a2a [OPTIONS] <input> <output>

Options:
  -h, --help      Show help message
  -v, --verbose   Verbose output
  -V, --version   Show version
  -f, --force     Overwrite output if exists
  -q, --quality   Quality for images/audio (1-100)
  --ocr           Enable OCR for image-to-text
  --dry-run       Preview conversion without executing
